/*
PURPOSE:
  Detect sustained failure pressure over time.
WHY:
  Single spikes are noise; rolling averages reveal degradation.

ASSUMPTIONS:
  - Short-term noise should be smoothed
  - Rolling window length controls sensitivity

DESIGN NOTES:
  - Rolling average is preferred over sum
  - Window size must match SLA sensitivity
*/

| timechart span=1h sum(is_failure) AS failures BY service
| untable _time service failures
| streamstats window=6 avg(failures) AS rolling_pressure BY service
